data.description: Discover your haven in this 4-bed, 2.5-bath beauty sprawling across 1.05 acres, offering the best of city life with a laid-back country vibe. The 2263 sq ft interior is a perfect blend of spaciousness and coziness, with an open concept living room, kitchen, and dining area surrounding a cozy wood-burning fireplace—ideal for gatherings. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, double ovens, and custom wood cabinets, creating a chef's dream come true. Step outside to a vast backyard with mature trees, a large deck under a stylish gazebo for entertaining, and a firepit for cozy evenings under the stars. All of this, coming in at less than $120 per sq ft, is a rare find! Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful and unique house your forever home.
